<SPT><TTL>UNIT PRICE</TTL><BRK/>
<NTE><BRK/>
<AST/><BRK/>
<NPR>NOTE:  The unit price for thermal desorption should be based on in-situ volume.  
For liquids and sludges the unit of measure should be mass.  Materials requiring 
retreatment should be segregated from treated materials.</NPR><BRK/>
