<TXT>Installation shall be performed with minimal damage to the existing site environment.  Welding shall be performed 
in accordance with <RID>AWS D1.1/D1.1M</RID> by welders certified to have passed qualification tests using procedures covered 
in <RID>AWS B2.1/B2.1M</RID> or <RID>ASME BPVC SEC IX</RID>.  Require any welder to retake the test when, in the opinion of the Contracting 
Officer, the work creates reasonable doubt as to the welder's proficiency.</TXT><BRK/>
<BRK/></SPT>
